# Pin specific repos to specific color slots.
# Format: <repo-key> <slot>
# Any whitespace works as separator. Blank lines and # comments are ignored.
#
# Repo-key is the basename of the project. For bare-worktree layouts
# (project/.bare + project/<branch> subdirs), all worktrees of the same
# project share one key (e.g. "platform", not "platform/main").
#
# Available slots (catppuccin-latte muted accents):
#   pink mauve red maroon peach yellow green teal sky blue lavender
#
# A pin is a hint: if another open window is already using the pinned slot
# for a different repo, the probe picks a different slot for this one.

.dotfiles         green
alice-supermarket yellow
cape              mauve
greppa            maroon
grove             pink
notebox           sky
platform          red
scripts           peach
tau               teal
